This turned out to be some sort of re-release. All three seasons had warped amd rippled covers that made it impossible to put back in the slipcase. I have since bought each season individually and the DVD's in this package are also packaged differently. Every season had at least two DVD's that didn't work properly and wouldn't play on ant DVD players. I would recommend just buying each season individually seeing as it's only about 1-2 dollars more expensive.
